  "remarks": "Mayor of Eslamshahr until 2020. Former Iranian MP. Former Governor-General (\"Farmandar\") of Tehran Province until Sep 2010, he was responsible for the intervention of police forces and therefore for the repression of demonstrations. He received a prize in Dec 2010 for his role in the post-election repression.",
